3.2 Current Market Condition

Most commercially available assistants are marketed as if they were CMA-3 and used as if they were CMA-4, while documented as if they were CMA-1 and legally disclaimed as if they were CMA-0.

This is not a certification model.

It is a fog machine with a subscription tier.

